NAME

DateTime::Locale::et_EE - Locale data examples for the Estonian Estonia (et-EE) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Estonian Estonia locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = teisipäev, 5. veebruar 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = reede, 22. detsember 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = laupäev, 15. september -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. veebruar 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. detsember 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. september -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. veebr 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. dets 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. sept -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05.02.08
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22.12.95
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15.09.-10
